data.revised_prompt: Create a hyper-realistic image of this scenario: A fantastical realm where the concept of death has disappeared is seeping into our known reality. To halt this crossover, a group of interstellar guardians must employ the aid of an imposing figure, their former adversary who is widely reputed for his destructive actions. This monumental task is distributed over six chapters. The narrative poses a question: Will this infamous destroyer find redemption, or bring about the ruin of all that exist? Note: This prompt has been modified to exclude any explicit references to copyrighted material.
